******************* PHASE 01 ******************* 

OBJECTIVE

CLI-based tool, txt/csv-based database, outputs one random airport in France, identified at least by its 4-letter ICAO code, output printed to the console



REQUIREMENTS

REQ_01 - The tool must run as an unprivileged local user on Windows

REQ_02 - The tool must output a unique airport, identified at least by its 4-letter ICAO code;

REQ_03 - The tool includes its own offline (but updateable) database of airports; The database must only include airports modelized in MSFS 2024